title: Google\Cloud\ManagedIdentities\V1\Domain
name: Domain
description:
Represents a managed Microsoft Active Directory domain.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.managedidentities.v1.Domain

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

methods.name: __construct
methods.description: Constructor.

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.name
params.description: Required. The unique name of the domain using the form: projects/{project_id}/locations/global/domains/{domain_name}.

params.name: data.labels
params.description: Optional. Resource labels that can contain user-provided metadata.

params.name: data.authorized_networks
params.description: Optional. The full names of the Google Compute Engine networks the domain instance is connected to. Networks can be added using UpdateDomain. The domain is only available on networks listed in authorized_networks. If CIDR subnets overlap between networks, domain creation will fail.

params.name: data.reserved_ip_range
params.description: Required. The CIDR range of internal addresses that are reserved for this domain. Reserved networks must be /24 or larger. Ranges must be unique and non-overlapping with existing subnets in [Domain].[authorized_networks].

params.name: data.locations
params.description: Required. Locations where domain needs to be provisioned. [regions][compute/docs/regions-zones/] e.g. us-west1 or us-east4 Service supports up to 4 locations at once. Each location will use a /26 block.

params.name: data.admin
params.description: Optional. The name of delegated administrator account used to perform Active Directory operations. If not specified, setupadmin will be used.

params.name: data.fqdn
params.description: Output only. The fully-qualified domain name of the exposed domain used by clients to connect to the service. Similar to what would be chosen for an Active Directory set up on an internal network.

params.name: data.create_time
params.description: Output only. The time the instance was created.

params.name: data.update_time
params.description: Output only. The last update time.

params.name: data.state
params.description: Output only. The current state of this domain.

params.name: data.status_message
params.description: Output only. Additional information about the current status of this domain, if available.

params.name: data.trusts
params.description: Output only. The current trusts associated with the domain.
